		* definition: a set of sets such that
			* it is closed under binary intersection
			* complementer is semiclosed
				* forall member sets. its complementer is a finite union of member sets
	* "algebra of sets" is a set of sets closed for finite union and intersection
		* algebras are semialgebras
		* note:
			* 'finite' here includes 0
